            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>François Dupuis Recreation Centre is a one stop shop for all your fitness needs. We have two beautiful pools: a 25-metre 6 lane pool and a leisure pool, both with ramp entry for easy access plus a dry sauna. Jennifer Stead's artwork,&nbsp;Water, runs along the pool viewing area.&nbsp;Check out our Fitness and Cardio centre equipped with the latest technology, including a NuStep machine. We offer a variety of programs for everyone in the family in our three multipurpose rooms.&nbsp;</p>
